The others are still going on, just as El Manana of Nuevo Laredo did after killing its director in 2004.
In 2010, Diario de Ciudad Juarez addressed drug cartels publicly with a front-page article entitled "What do you want from us"?
Some journalists have fled their homes or even across the border.
It's a difficult decision.
